{{Infobox Union |name= UGTD |country= [[Djibouti]] |affiliation= |members= |full_name= General Union of Djibouti Workers |native_name= Union Générale des Travailleurs de Djibouti |image= |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= |people= [[Kamil Diraneth Hared]], general secretary |website= |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''General Union of Djibouti Workers''' (UGTD) is a [[trade union]] centre in [[Djibouti]]. It was the official union arm of the government until 1995, when protests and conflicts separated the two. The UGTD now works closely with the [[Union of Djibouti Workers|UDT]].
